@node Description "Description"

PROGRAMM: ACD V1.0
AUTHOR:   SMC of AbYsS
DATE:     07.08.1994
CLASS:    Freeware

Description:

                ACD is a very simple Tool for CLI Freaks.
                (which don't know KINGCON or else !).
                It works like the CD Command from the Work-
                bench (which is in ROM under Kick 2.0+).

                The main difference is that a Requester
                asks for the new Directory. So this Tool
                COULD be useful when you have longer Dir
                names and don't have any KINGCON-like
                Tools running.

                May you can change by giving a Dirname.


                USAGE:  ACD [Directory|Assign] [?]


                NO PARAMETER MEANS REQUESTER SELECTION !!!

                [Directory|Assign] <Destination

                [?] <If you use this, a short Info
                     will be shown.



@endnode

@node History "History"


        History & Bugs:

                V1.0    + [only] ASL-Library Interface
                        + ?-Info available
                        + Destination Path selelction by
                          Requester

                        Bugs:

                        - If you change Dir by giving a
                          name, the name you give appears
                          in the PROMPT line.




@endnode

@node Requirements "Requirements"


        Requirements:

                - ASL.Library, so it only runs under
                - Kick 2.0+.



@endnode


@node Future "Future Ideas"


        Future Ideas:

                - complete ReqTools-Interface for Requester.
                  [in V1.2]
                  As far as I know you can use it under older
                  Kicks too.
                - minor bug corrections.
                  [in V1.2]
                - better PARAMETER Support.
                  [in V1.2/V1.3]
                - LOCALE Support
                  [in V1.3 or never]


@endnode

